joshprk/nixos
-------------

personal nixos configuration, with

  - agenix secrets encryption
  - impermanence
  - tmpfs in-ram root
  - btrfs with zstd compression
  - luks encryption with tpm unlock
  - secure boot support
  - xdg base directory compliant home directory
  - nixvim configuration
  - hyprland configuration
  - develop command with globally available dev shells
  - support for gaming through flatpaks with nvidia support
  - declared nmcli networks through nix
  - pure and stateless

  feel free to contact me on discord at joshprk with any questions
